solution:
After adiabatic compression, the volume of the gas is reduced by $1\%$, i.e., $\frac{V_{f}}{V_{i}}=0.99$. The partial pressures of He gas and $\mathrm{N}_{2}$ gas are given by

$$
p_{1 f}=p_{1 i}\left(\frac{V_{i}}{V_{f}}\right)^{\gamma_{1}}, \quad p_{2 f}=p_{2 i}\left(\frac{V_{i}}{V_{f}}\right)^{\gamma_{2}}
$$

Substituting the data, we calculate

$$
\begin{aligned}
& p_{1 f}=0.625 \mathrm{~atm} \\
& p_{2 f}=1.247 \mathrm{~atm}
\end{aligned}
$$

The pressure of the mixed gas after adiabatic compression is

$$
p_{f}=p_{1 f}+p_{2 f}=1.87 \mathrm{~atm}
$$

$$
\begin{aligned}
& S = -\left(\frac{\partial G}{\partial T}\right)_{p} = \frac{5}{2} R - R \ln \left[\frac{a p}{(R T)^{5/2}}\right] \\
& c_p = T\left(\frac{\partial S}{\partial T}\right)_{p} = \frac{5}{2} R
\end{aligned}
$$

如果取初始容器中气体的质量为 $M$ ，活门打开后立即关闭，设有 $\Delta M$ 气体经活门跑出去，以留在容器中质量为 $M-\Delta M$ 的气体作为考虑的系统，则从（1） $\rightarrow$ （2）为绝热膨胀过程，从（2） $\rightarrow$ （3）为等容过程。在绝热过程（1） $\rightarrow$ （2）和等容过程（2） $\rightarrow$ （3）中选取 $T, p$ 作为状态变量，得：

$$
\begin{aligned}
p_{1}^{\frac{1}{\gamma}-1} T_{0} & =p_{0}^{\frac{1}{\gamma}-1} T_{2} \\
\frac{T_{2}}{T_{0}} & =\frac{p_{0}}{p_{2}}
\end{aligned}
$$

两式联立，解得：

$$
\left(\frac{1}{\gamma}-1\right) \ln \frac{p_{1}}{p_{0}}=\ln \frac{p_{0}}{p_{2}}
$$

由此得

$$
\gamma=\frac{\ln p_{1}-\ln p_{0}}{\ln p_{1}-\ln p_{2}}
$$

在标准状态下 \(\text{CO}_{2}\) 气体分子的数密度为 \(n_{0}=2.69 \times 10^{25} / \text{m}^3\)。  
开始时，每秒通过管子中点的横截面从右到左的分子数  

\[ 
\begin{aligned}
\frac{\mathrm{d} N_{2}}{\mathrm{d} t} & =\frac{1}{6} n_{2} \bar{v} \Delta S=\frac{1}{12} n_{0} \bar{v} \Delta S\left(1-\frac{2 \bar{\lambda}}{l}\right)=\frac{1}{12} n_{0} \sqrt{\frac{8 R T}{\pi \mu}} \Delta S\left(1-\frac{2 \bar{\lambda}}{l}\right) \\
& =7.94 \times 10^{22}-4.94 \times 10^{15} \, \text{s}^{-1} \approx 7.94 \times 10^{22} \, \text{s}^{-1}
\end{aligned} 
\]

式中 \(n_{2} \approx \frac{n_{0}}{2}\left(1-\frac{2 \bar{\lambda}}{l}\right)\) 是 \(x=\frac{l}{2}+\bar{\lambda}\) 处的放射性分子数密度。

在等压过程中系统内能的改变

$$
\begin{aligned}
\Delta U & = \Delta H - p \Delta V = \Delta H - p m \left(V_{\text{汽}} - V_{\text{液}}\right) \\
& = 5.417 \times 10^{4} - 1.013 \times 10^{5} \times 0.018 \times \left(1.673 - 1.043 \times 10^{-3}\right) \\
& = 5.112 \times 10^{4} \mathrm{~J}
\end{aligned}
$$
